OL,6,FA mum who was diagnosed with carbon
OL,7,Fmonoxide poisoning as a result of her
OL,8,Ffaulty boiler says she was "horrified"
OL,9,Fafter doctors suspected her symptoms
OL,10,Fwere caused by cocaine abuse.
OL,12,FFor three years, Sue Westwood-
OL,13,FRuttledge, 52, suffered a range of
OL,14,Fsymptoms which resulted in her major
OL,15,Forgans beginning to shut down.
OL,17,FThe mum-of two's main symptoms
OL,18,Fincluded headaches, dizziness and a
OL,19,Flack of concentration.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
