OL,3,CMum accused of cocaine abuse prior to
OL,4,Ccarbon monoxide poisoning diagnosis
OL,6,F"Investigations found the flue wasn't
OL,7,Fconnected under the built-in wardrobes
OL,8,Fin the master bedroom and the
OL,9,Fconnectors in the boiler cupboard,
OL,10,Fwhich were one metre from my office
OL,11,Fand Josh's bedroom, were the wrong
OL,12,Fones, so CO was leaking from there as
OL,13,Fwell. I was being poisoned during the
OL,14,Fday in my office then at night in my
OL,15,Fbed."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
