OL,3,CMum accused of cocaine abuse prior to
OL,4,Ccarbon monoxide poisoning diagnosis
OL,6,FShe has now joined a call for new
OL,7,Fsafety rules and awareness by carbon
OL,8,Fmonoxide charity CO-Gas Safety, which
OL,9,Festimates that around 20 per cent of
OL,10,Fhouseholds could have dangerous levels
OL,11,Fof carbon monoxide.
OL,13,FShe said: "I underwent an Alzheimer's
OL,14,Ftest, and the Professor at the memory
OL,15,Fclinic told me that my results were
OL,16,Fcomparable to those of someone in
OL,17,Ftheir 80s. And he likened my ongoing
OL,18,Fproblems to someone who had suffered a
OL,19,Fstroke.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
