OL,6,FSue still suffers from the
OL,7,Fdevastating, long-term consequences of
OL,8,Fher three-year exposure to the deadly
OL,9,Fgas - dubbed the "silent killer". She
OL,10,Fhad to give up her business because of
OL,11,Fdamage the CO caused to her brain.
OL,13,FSue now also has a range of conditions
OL,14,Fincluding fibromyalgia, Tietzes
OL,15,FSyndrome, debilitating migraines, and
OL,16,Fmemory issues.
OL,26,@qD@ROUqD@`O]
