OL,6,FShe has also had operations on both
OL,7,Fhands and feet because nerve damage
OL,8,Fand had to retrain herself to read
OL,9,Fbecause for years she couldn't read
OL,10,Fmore than a short paragraph of text.
OL,12,FStephanie Trotter OBE, president and
OL,13,Fdirector of the CO-Gas Safety charity,
OL,14,Fsaid: "The life-changing effects
OL,15,Fcaused by the poor installation of
OL,16,FSue's boiler and its associated
OL,17,Fpipework in a brand-new property was
OL,18,Fshocking and completely avoidable.
OL,26,@vD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
