OL,3,CMum accused of cocaine abuse prior to
OL,4,Ccarbon monoxide poisoning diagnosis
OL,6,F"Sue had no tests for CO poisoning,
OL,7,Fdespite her symptoms hospitalising her
OL,8,Ftwice. Nor did her GP recognise
OL,9,Fpossible symptoms in Josh.
OL,11,F"The All-Party Parliamentary Carbon
OL,12,FMonoxide Group (APPCOG) now has a
OL,13,Fmedical committee which, after several
OL,14,Fyears, seems now to have good
OL,15,Fknowledge. However, where is the
OL,16,Fawareness PR campaign to properly
OL,17,Falert medical professionals at all
OL,18,Flevels?"
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUzD@HO]
